<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">

    <script>
        (function() {
            const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'system';
            if (savedTheme === 'dark' || (savedTheme === 'system' && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
            } else {
                document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-theme');
            }
        })();
    </script>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="bg-pattern-overlay"></div>

    <header>
        <div class="site-title">
            <img src="/icon.png" alt="Awing Logo" class="header-logo">
            <span>exlore<span class="title-name">AWING</span></span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/origin">Origins</a></li>
                <li><a href="/meals">Meals</a></li>
                <li><a href="/customs">Customs</a></li>
            </ul>

            <div class="theme-switch-container">
                <select id="themeSelector" class="theme-select">
                    <option value="light">Light Theme</option>
                    <option value="dark">Dark Theme</option>
                    <option value="system">Match System</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <script>
        const themeSelector = document.getElementById('themeSelector');

        // Initializing the select value according to localStorage
        const currentTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'system';
        themeSelector.value = currentTheme;

        function applyTheme(theme) {
            if (theme === 'dark') {
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
            } else if (theme === 'light') {
                document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-theme');
            } else {
                // Match Device Mode
                if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches) {
                    document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
                } else {
                    document.documentElement.removeAttribute('data-theme');
                }
            }
        }

        // Listen to manual change from the user
        themeSelector.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
            const selected = e.target.value;
            localStorage.setItem('theme', selected);
            applyTheme(selected);
        });

        // Listen to automatic changes from the device if it's in match device mode
        window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').addEventListener('change', () => {
            if (localStorage.getItem('theme') === 'system' || !localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
                applyTheme('system');
            }
        });
    </script>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>The <span class="txt-gold">Cultural Architecture</span> of <span class="txt-gold">Awing</span> .</h1>
        <p>A refined repository of historical lineages, sovereign culinary arts, and ancestral laws belonging to the
            Awing Kingdom, situated in the North-West Region of Cameroon.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="container">

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">01 / History</span>
                <h2>Origins & Sacred Lineage</h2>
                <p>Explore the deep Tikar migrations, the early foundations of the Santa subdivision fondoms, and
                    the ancient spiritual convenants surrounding the Lake Awing sanctuary.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/origin" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Records &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">02 / Gastronomy</span>
                <h2>Royal Culinary Arts</h2>
                <p>Discover the precise traditional chemistry of the Achuh yellow soup, limestone pairings, and the
                    complex etiquette of royal banquets.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/meals" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Gallery &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">03 / Sovereignity</span>
                <h2>Customs & Secret Societies</h2>
                <p>An introduction to the legislative roles of the Nchinda noble circles, palace protocols, and the
                    ancestral steps of the Keleng dance.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/customs" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Customs &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy 2026 Awing Cultural Project &bull; Academic Programming Assignment</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>